This API endpoint is used to make an HTTP POST request to retrieve an access token from Amazon's authentication server. The request should include the necessary credentials and parameters in the x-www-form-urlencoded format.

### Request Body Parameters
- No specific request body parameters were provided.

### Response
The response of this request can be documented as a JSON schema. It will include the structure and data types of the response fields, providing a clear understanding of the expected response format.

